\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F83%2FExecutiveDecision_poster.jpg&h=3f3df4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.六年前，竊車界中綽號「曼菲斯」的藍道雷恩斯，乃是一位技術頂尖的偷車賊，不但行竊過程從來未曾失手過，最快的行竊速度紀錄是六十秒，而且法律無法制裁他。但是，曼菲斯的母親十分擔心他弟弟藍道奇普會受到他影響，而步上後塵，勸戒他能就此停手，毅然從竊車界中退休，過著平凡的生活..<br />\n<br />\n2.一架載滿400名乘客的波音747從希臘雅典起飛前往美國華盛頓首府的途中，被一群由阿拉伯人納吉&middot;哈森帶領的恐怖份子挾持，要求美國釋放他們的首腦艾爾&middot;沙耶&middot;亞法，否則將在華盛頓上空引爆機上的毒氣彈，摧毀美國東岸超過四千萬條人命..<br />\n<br />\n12 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=k1mwhY0xzbygSZy31giZGDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=80a56c7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=k1mwhY0xzbygSZy31giZGDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=369c16c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4169b6c0450d7ce5e921eb5b739aee8d9b003a6","tid":868632,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82259f4671a861a3ef27fd3531a397fd6cffb3df","tid":868632,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /